# Summary
This documentation page describes the Userflow destination integration with Amplitude, which allows syncing user cohorts from Amplitude to Userflow for targeted in-app experiences (product tours, checklists, surveys) without coding, and enables bidirectional data flow where user interactions in Userflow can be streamed back to Amplitude.

